To seek refuge from it we wrote a letter to the editor of daily Amroz and asked â€œwhat should we do after matriculation exams that we donâ€™t have to go through strenuous physical labor.
Editor in his reply wrote that we should become a doctor or an engineer and should opt for such and such subjects to study.
